column1: # N.B. To make mangrove swamps look the way they're supposed to, use MANGROVE rather than BEACH constants
# N.B. Thanks to biome blending, unilib:sand_silt and unilib:dirt_silt_fine occur at higher
#   elevations than MANGROVE_MAX. Place a few mangrove trees there, to avoid bald patches

# In the "gaia" remix, this is an uncommon item spawning on ordinary sand, near water. Thanks to the
#   "deco_gaia_papyrus" package, it can be farmed on several dirt/sand nodes

# "produce_pineapple" is common in hot_humid biomes, as a thematic decoration as well as a food
#   source. "produce_cocoa_jungle" generates on jungle tree trunks. Additional "produce_onion_wild"
